  "description": {
    "zh": "雷猴，最近一个疑似是Dealmaker的熟人来找我。真他妈时髦，穿着西装，带着一个瓶盖大的戒指。我曾在聚会上见过他一次，他常开一辆宝马。\n 他说不管是有没有战争，他都会尽量活的精致些。恩，也许并不是精致，更像是一种逃避现实。所以给我找些珠宝来，我得拿来应付他。记得再搞点劳力土手表，买一送一，质量不太好的也可以。但，相信我，兄弟。对于这种人来说，最好是完好无损的。\n",
    "en": "Salam, there's a new sweet deal for you. Recently, I was approached by the guy who’s some sort of Reshala’s acquaintance. Posh as fuck, in a suit, and with a signet on his finger the size of a bottle cap. I’ve seen him at some gathering once, he used to drive a black BMW. He says that war or no war, his crib's gotta be all ornamented. Well, not exactly a crib, more like a hideout. Fetch me a bunch of jewelry, and I’ll hand it over to him. Look for horse statues, cats, lions, all that stuff. And look for Roler watches, the golden ones, it will be a complimentary gift: It’s best to be on good terms with such people, believe me, brother. Don't let me down, brother, or we're both in trouble."
  },
